description_top: Collection of philosophical texts (Averroës and Themistius on Aristotle)
catalogue_description: Hebrew and Judaica Manuscripts at the Bodleian Libraries, Oxford University
title: Collection of philosophical texts (Averroës and Themistius on Aristotle)
author: Themistius
description: Contents: Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's Physica auscultatio (ff. 1r-33r). Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's De Coelo et Mundo (ff. 33v-57r). Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's De Generatione et Corruptione (ff. 57v-65v). Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's Meteorologica (ff. 66r-92v). Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's De Anima (ff. 93r-116r). Averroës, Paraphrase of Aristotle's De Sensu et Sensibili (ff. 116v-133v). Themistius, Commentary on book Δ of Aristotle's Metaphysics (ff. 134r-151v). Averroës, Epitomes of Books 1-4 of Aristotle's Metaphysics (ff. 152r-192v).
